================================================================================
Upstream and reference sources
================================================================================

The wizards reference (without redistributing) the following public frameworks
and standards. Consult each source for authoritative, up-to-date text.

  * CoSAI Shared Responsibility Framework (CoSAI, OASIS Open)
  * CSA AI Controls Matrix (AICM) v1.0.3 (Cloud Security Alliance)
  * OWASP Top 10 for LLM Applications, 2025 Edition (OWASP Foundation)
  * NIST AI Risk Management Framework and NISTIR 8605A (NIST)
  * MITRE ATLAS / AML threat taxonomy (MITRE)
  * NIST CSF 2.0, NIST SP 800-53r5, SP 800-207, SP 800-218 and related
    publications (NIST)

Trademarks and logos of the above organisations remain the property of their
respective owners.
